query:
SELECT 
  at.id as auditTypeId,
  at.auditName,
  at.auditCategory,
  atem.id as templateId,
  atem.templateName,
  atem.isActive
FROM auditTypes at
LEFT JOIN auditTemplates atem ON at.id = atem.auditTypeId
WHERE at.auditName LIKE '%Daily%'
ORDER BY at.id;
